nd she was as clever and smart as she was lovely.<br>
<br>
When Kehli was just blossoming into womanhood, her peaceful life of contemplation and study was destroyed.<br>
<br>
Her parents, on vacation in lovely Kithicor Forest, were brutally killed by wandering undeads.  Kehli was suddenly homeless, alone in all of Norrath.<br>
<br>
She was soon befriended by a lovely halfling Lucyokk, and her bizarre sidekicks, Ndrokk the gnome, and Kogginn the dwarf.<br>
<br>
Despite being taught at an early age to avoid the lesser races, she came to love and trust her new companions as family (except the drawf - NEVER trust a DWARF!)<br>
<br>
She travelled all over Norrath, calling nowhere home, as the lovely city of Erudin held such painful memories.  On her journeys, she met many incredible people.<br>
<br>
The dashing bad ass Goht, the wise Kordail, the ugly-yet-appealing Styrogur and his lovely Styrona.<br>
<br>
The magnetic Thornfist, the wickedly skilled Zoldarf, the enigmatic Salornx, the talented Ozz and the charming couple of Mac and Lelana.....so many memories of more people than she can list.....<br>
<br>
Then it happened one day in Oasis, she met Braydin Firecaster, an unparallelled specimen of Erudite manliness... the wit! the looks! the adorable mini earth elemental - she was smitten!<br>
<br>
They were wed, with many of their dearest friends in attendance, and all was well, or was it????<br>
<br>
Incredibly, Kehli's father had strayed from his vows! He had fathered a bastard daugher with a voluptious and evil temptress in Paineel.  This sister grew twisted and bitter under the constant tutelage of her mother.  She was named Baddream, and her only goal in life is to out do her hated pampered sibling!<br>
<br>
Baddream grew up the hard way, playing in the dark warrens with the bones of the playmates she slew as she grew weary of them.  She had no group, no powerful benefactors to see her into her teens, her twenties, she did it the hard way - alone.  Sure there were pickups, some went well, many left her naked and afraid far from home.  She was last seen being shredded by guards in High Hold while screaming &quot; I hate you KEHLI!!!&quot;<br>
<br>
What does her future hold? <p><HTML><BODY>
