<br>
She was restless now, and sleep eluded her.  She paced anxiously in the modest accommodations in North Freeport.  She found the time apart from her beloved difficult, but she understood his need to expore the arcane in places she could not travel.  He would not be back this day, and she felt very much alone.<br>
<br>
A sudden scratching at her door startled her, and she swore softly in Erudite as she approached the door.<br>
<br>
It wasnt quite dawn, and the hall was dark as she opened the door.  In the dimness she saw a figure in a black robe  - and for a heartstopping instant, she could see no face!<br>
<br>
Despite her powers, her vast experience with terrifying monsters , she stepped back, and gasped aloud.<br>
<br>
The faceless spectre stepped into her room and the light hit the smirking face of her half sister.<br>
<br>
&quot;Nervous Kehli?&quot; she whispered, smiling.<br>
<br>
&quot;Just startled Dream, I.. I just woke up&quot; Kehli was angry now with the way she was behaving.  She was no tender child to shy away from shadows! She was a mature woman, with many seasons of hunting dangerous creatures!<br>
<br>
&quot; I brought your breakfast &quot; she placed a tray on the small table.<br>
<br>
Instead of being pleased with the gesture, Kehli was suddenly uneasy.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Wha ... ahem.. what is it?&quot; she wanted Dream to go, she suddenly felt naked and trapped.<br>
<br>
&quot;Just some pie, it wont bite you&quot;  she was grinning now, a strange gleam in her eyes.  She chuckled as she walked to the door, shaking her head.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Have a nice day&quot; she whispered, as she left the room without looking back, shutting the door softly behind her.  <br>
<br>
Kehli began to shake, and crossed the room swiftly and bolted the door.  She looked at the tray on her table and felt the bile rise in her throat.<br>
<br>
She had wanted to help her sister. Kehli had initiated the contact between them, and since Dream had joined the Champions of Kaos there had been only cordial conversation between them.<br>
<br>
Why was she suddenly so very afraid? <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub65.ezboard.com/femarr80492frm16.showNextMessage?topicID=1.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/femarr80492frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/femarr80492frm16.emailToFriend?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/femarr80492frm16.threadControl?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/femarr80492frm16.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/femarr80492frm16.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub65.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="emarr80492frm4">Announcements<option value="emarr80492frm2">General<option value="emarr80492frm3">Raids<option value="emarr80492frm5">Buy/Sell/Trade or better yet give it away!<option value="emarr80492frm10">/OOC and Funny Stories<option value="emarr80492frm11">CofK Members only<option value="emarr80492frm12">Officer Chat<option value="emarr80492frm13">Epics<option value="emarr80492frm